stix:STIX_Header.stix:Title: Spear-phishing Campaign Targeting Government Agencies and Centers of Academic Excellence
stix:STIX_Header.stix:Description: A government agency reported spear-phishing emails from known CNE operators that contained likely malicious links between 11 and 12 February 2016. The activity was mitigated, and additional details about the links were not provided.

stix:Indicator.indicator:Title: Malicious E-mail Indicator
stix:Indicator.indicator:Description:
